{"tid":848993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血巴打自資為全港屋邨球場掛籃網：享受「灌籃」樂趣","createTime":"2018-10-05T10:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T11:30:04.000Z","uid":75969,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b88d2e9d3e7e43a2fffaedb976c73eeb19cddfaa","tid":848993,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T10:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2170000/2171377/cheung_thumb_20181003_ch_v2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2170000%2F2171377%2Fcheung_thumb_20181003_ch_v2_1024.jpg&h=4dc3bf07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我想幫全港屋邨籃球場掛上籃網！」25歲的張夕楓（夕Sir）眼見許多公共屋邨籃球場籃網破爛或消失，街坊入球不爽，在連登討論區招募義工，決心自掏腰包為全港屋邨球場掛上籃網。即使被潑冷水，孤身行動，他也堅持完成目標，甚至希望設計一種籃球運動，讓大眾不被高度限制，享受「灌籃」樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2171377/%E7%86%B1%E8%A1%80%E5%B7%B4%E6%89%93%E8%87%AA%E8%B3%87%E7%82%BA%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%8B%E9%82%A8%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4%E6%8E%9B%E7%B1%83%E7%B6%B2%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%AB%E5%8F%97%E3%80%8C%E7%81%8C%E7%B1%83%E3%80%8D%E6%A8%82%E8%B6%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2171377%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A1%2580%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B3%2587%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B1%258B%25E9%2582%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%258E%259B%25E7%25B1%2583%25E7%25B6%25B2%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E5%258F%2597%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%2581%258C%25E7%25B1%2583%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25B6%25A3&d=gwG7drdNM5ZKCF2S7esmDGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=004e2783\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2171377/%E7%86%B1%E8%A1%80%E5%B7%B4%E6%89%93%E8%87%AA%E8%B3%87%E7%82%BA%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E5%B1%8B%E9%82%A8%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4%E6%8E%9B%E7%B1%83%E7%B6%B2%EF%BC%9A%E4%BA%AB%E5%8F%97%E3%80%8C%E7%81%8C%E7%B1%83%E3%80%8D%E6%A8%82%E8%B6%A3</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打個post:<br />\n我想幫全屋村籃球場掛上